<h2>Discover Risotto</h2>
<p>Risotto is an Italian dish, a classic comfort food that has gained international popularity. Risotto is a rice-based
  dish, with Arborio rice being the most commonly used variety. What sets risotto apart is the method of preparation,
  involving a slow and gradual addition of liquid to the rice, which results in a creamy consistency while maintaining a
  distinct bite. Risotto is perfect because it's versatile, allowing for a wide range of flavor variations.</p>
